item.description: Time for another week log. Compiler: As this was finals week at my University, I was unable to do much work on the compiler. I stubbed out some of the logic for the analyzer, and made plans to move from a tokenizer/parser combo to a streaming parser. This should simplify some of the logic in the parser. Website: Moved over one old entry, as requested in an e-mail.
